# Implementation Plan: AWS S3 Incident Post-Mortem Generation

Integrate AWS S3 and Amazon Bedrock Claude 3.5 Sonnet into the FastAPI backend using `boto3` to generate, upload, and serve pre-signed download URLs for Incident Post-Mortem Markdown reports upon incident resolution.

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> The backend will use `boto3` to generate Post-Mortem Markdown reports via Claude 3.5 Sonnet, upload them to an AWS S3 bucket (`s3.put_object`), generate 1-hour pre-signed S3 download URLs (`s3.generate_presigned_url`), and stream the URL via WebSocket to render a glowing download button on the frontend.

