#### [NEW] [s3_client.py](file:///c:/Users/saake/Downloads/sentinel-agent-main/sentinel-agent-main/backend/s3_client.py)
- Implement `generate_post_mortem(incident_data: dict) -> tuple[str, str]`:
  1. Invokes Claude 3.5 Sonnet via Bedrock runtime or structured template to synthesize outage summary, root cause, and applied remediation into Markdown.
